EFF leader Julius Malema says the Finance Minister Malusi Gigaba is a facilitator of state capture JOHANNESBURG - EFF leader Julius Malema says the party will open criminal charges against Finance Minister Malusi Gigaba who he says is a facilitator of state capture.He also warned the DA it would withdraw its votes in municipalities if the party didn't suspend Helen Zille as premier of Western Cape.Malema is briefing the media on 'Zuma-Gupta family' corruption claims.WATCH LIVE: Malema claims more Zuma-Gupta corruptionMore details to follow.